\Delta_k = E_k - 1
 E_1 = (1 + \Delta_{1/n})^{n} 
k
\Delta_k f \approx k \frac{df}{dx}
 E_1 \approx \left(1 + \frac{1}{n} \frac{d}{dx} \right)^n 
n
 E_1 = \lim_{n \to \infty} \left(1 + \frac{1}{n} \frac{d}{dx} \right)^n = e^{d/dx}
e^{t \frac d{dx}} f(x) = f(x+t)
e^{0 \frac d{dx}}
\frac d{dt} [e^{t \frac d{dx}} f(x)] \big|_{t=0} = f'(x)
